ZH: 我们如果不赶快出发，否则会错过火车。
EN: If we don't leave soon, otherwise we will miss the train.

ZH: 你必须好好学习，否则无法取得好成绩。
EN: You must study hard, otherwise you won't achieve good grades.

ZH: 如果你不小心，否则会摔倒。
EN: If you're not careful, otherwise you'll fall down.

ZH: 我们应该多做运动，否则会导致健康问题。
EN: We should exercise more, otherwise it can lead to health issues.

ZH: 如果我不提醒他们，否则他们会忘记出席会议。
EN: If I don't remind them, otherwise they will forget to attend the meeting.

ZH: 如果你不遵守交通规则，否则会面临罚款。
EN: If you don't follow the traffic rules, otherwise you will face a fine.

ZH: 如果你不好好休息，否则会影响工作效率。
EN: If you don't rest well, otherwise it will affect your work efficiency.

ZH: 我们必须及时支付账单，否则会被取消服务。
EN: We must pay the bills on time, otherwise the service will be canceled.

ZH: 如果你不按时提交作业，否则会影响你的成绩。
EN: If you don't submit your assignments on time, otherwise it will affect your grades.

ZH: 如果你不好好照顾自己，否则会生病。
EN: If you don't take care of yourself properly, otherwise you will get sick.

ZH: 如果你不戴口罩，否则可能会感染疾病。
EN: If you don't wear a mask, otherwise you might get infected with a disease.

ZH: 我们应该注意饮食，否则会导致身体不适。
EN: We should pay attention to our diet, otherwise it may lead to physical discomfort.

ZH: 如果你不努力学习，否则将来会后悔。
EN: If you don't study hard, otherwise you will regret it in the future.

ZH: 如果你不断提出问题，否则你永远不会学到新知识。
EN: If you don't ask questions constantly, otherwise you will never learn new things.

ZH: 我们需要保护环境，否则会给未来的生活带来困难。
EN: We need to protect the environment, otherwise it will bring difficulties to future life.

ZH: 如果你不尊重他人，否则会失去他们的友谊。
EN: If you don't respect others, otherwise you will lose their friendship.

ZH: 你必须按规定的时间交货，否则会影响客户的信任。
EN: You must deliver the goods on time as per the regulations, otherwise it will affect the trust of the customers.

ZH: 如果你不关闭电器，否则会浪费能源。
EN: If you don't turn off the appliances, otherwise it will waste energy.

ZH: 如果你不足够专注，否则会出错。
EN: If you're not focused enough, otherwise mistakes will occur.

ZH: 如果我们不改善交通状况，否则将来会更加拥堵。
EN: If we don't improve the traffic conditions, otherwise it will be more congested in the future.
